text: Ivano-Kuvalat () is a rural locality (a selo) in Ivano-Kuvalatsky Selsoviet, Zilairsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 430 as of 2010. There are 7 streets. == Geography == It is located 57 km from Zilair. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zilairsky District
title: Ivano-Kuvalat
